WEBVTT

00:00:12.666 --> 00:00:14.291
Is everything going smoothly?

00:00:15.500 --> 00:00:16.125
Is there anything I can help with?

00:00:16.125 --> 00:00:16.916
Please let me know anytime.

00:00:31.541 --> 00:00:32.583
Miss Meilin.

00:00:33.041 --> 00:00:33.541
Oh.

00:00:34.291 --> 00:00:34.833
Hello.

00:00:35.166 --> 00:00:35.916
Hello there.

00:00:37.208 --> 00:00:38.458
Are you looking for a seat?

00:00:38.458 --> 00:00:38.791
Hmm.

00:00:38.791 --> 00:00:39.416
Yes.

00:00:40.083 --> 00:00:41.083
Uh...

00:00:41.666 --> 00:00:42.541
Then...

00:00:43.416 --> 00:00:44.333
please sit over here.

00:01:01.666 --> 00:01:02.166
You...

00:01:02.708 --> 00:01:04.916
do you like watching people draw?

00:01:08.791 --> 00:01:09.833
Actually...

00:01:09.833 --> 00:01:11.666
I like drawing myself...

00:01:12.666 --> 00:01:14.041
that's why I organized this event.

00:01:14.541 --> 00:01:15.041
Oh.

00:01:15.791 --> 00:01:17.166
You can draw too?

00:01:19.458 --> 00:01:20.666
What do you draw?

00:01:20.833 --> 00:01:22.416
Just doodling.

00:01:23.083 --> 00:01:24.291
Not as good as you.

00:01:24.791 --> 00:01:27.083
Don't say that until I see it.

00:01:27.083 --> 00:01:28.458
It's not very good.

00:02:07.916 --> 00:02:08.666
Wow.

00:02:10.666 --> 00:02:12.791
You call this doodling?

00:02:13.541 --> 00:02:15.708
It's so beautiful.

00:02:18.416 --> 00:02:19.416
Your lines...

00:02:19.791 --> 00:02:21.166
are so warm.

00:02:21.333 --> 00:02:22.083
It's just...

00:02:22.541 --> 00:02:23.541
when I'm bored...

00:02:23.541 --> 00:02:24.291
I draw to pass the time.

00:02:26.250 --> 00:02:27.750
I can't believe it.

00:02:28.208 --> 00:02:29.375
Someone like you...

00:02:29.375 --> 00:02:31.500
such a steady hotel manager...

00:02:32.750 --> 00:02:33.958
actually...

00:02:33.958 --> 00:02:36.083
has an artist living inside him too.

00:02:37.833 --> 00:02:39.541
Those drawings, I just...

00:02:39.916 --> 00:02:42.833
never found someone I wanted to share them with...

00:02:43.541 --> 00:02:44.541
until now.

00:03:03.916 --> 00:03:06.458
These are desserts provided by our hotel.

00:03:11.541 --> 00:03:12.333
Miss Meilin.

00:03:16.166 --> 00:03:16.916
Thank you.

00:03:39.083 --> 00:03:41.333
Fruits provided by our hotel.

00:04:03.125 --> 00:04:06.291
Did you find drawing inspiration today?

00:04:06.791 --> 00:04:07.291
Hmm.

00:04:07.541 --> 00:04:08.583
I found some.

00:04:16.291 --> 00:04:16.916
Today...

00:04:16.916 --> 00:04:19.958
maybe I used my brain too much...

00:04:19.958 --> 00:04:20.791
I'm starving.

00:04:21.416 --> 00:04:22.416
Uh...

00:04:22.416 --> 00:04:24.666
Then shall we go eat together?

00:04:25.291 --> 00:04:26.416
I just got off work.

00:04:26.708 --> 00:04:27.166
Hmm.

00:04:27.166 --> 00:04:27.791
Sure.

00:04:34.041 --> 00:04:35.166
Wow.

00:04:35.166 --> 00:04:36.416
What is this?

00:04:48.333 --> 00:04:49.541
Wow.

00:04:50.458 --> 00:04:51.833
Can you get used to this?

00:04:51.833 --> 00:04:53.083
What is this called?

00:04:53.541 --> 00:04:55.791
This is called Dancing Shrimp.

00:04:55.791 --> 00:04:57.458
It's considered... by Phayao Lake...

00:04:57.458 --> 00:04:59.166
a very famous specialty.

00:05:01.583 --> 00:05:02.166
Come on.

00:05:02.416 --> 00:05:03.041
Please.

00:05:03.416 --> 00:05:04.666
Then I'll have one.

00:05:14.916 --> 00:05:15.666
How is it?

00:05:17.375 --> 00:05:18.541
A bit strange.

00:05:18.791 --> 00:05:19.166
But...

00:05:19.166 --> 00:05:20.208
it's quite delicious.

00:05:22.958 --> 00:05:23.916
I'll try another one.

00:05:31.166 --> 00:05:32.666
Why are you just staring at me?

00:05:33.791 --> 00:05:35.291
This...

00:05:52.541 --> 00:05:53.916
I'm so full.

00:05:53.916 --> 00:05:55.416
But so happy.

00:05:57.541 --> 00:05:59.666
Do you want to go see other places?

00:05:59.666 --> 00:06:00.458
I do.

00:06:01.791 --> 00:06:02.541
Then...

00:06:03.541 --> 00:06:04.791
I'm off tomorrow.

00:06:05.291 --> 00:06:06.541
If you don't mind...

00:06:06.541 --> 00:06:07.416
I can...

00:06:07.416 --> 00:06:08.541
be your guide...

00:06:08.541 --> 00:06:09.458
and take you around.

00:06:09.458 --> 00:06:10.416
Really?

00:06:10.791 --> 00:06:11.666
Really.

00:06:12.291 --> 00:06:13.958
Then I don't mind at all.

00:06:13.958 --> 00:06:15.916
You definitely have to take me out.

00:06:17.583 --> 00:06:18.083
Then...

00:06:18.291 --> 00:06:20.166
let me see where we should go.

00:06:30.208 --> 00:06:30.916
Wow

00:06:31.583 --> 00:06:32.958
I think I've found it

00:06:32.958 --> 00:06:34.541
It's quite an interesting place

00:06:41.958 --> 00:06:43.916
I really like it here

00:06:44.666 --> 00:06:46.041
It's so quiet

00:06:48.291 --> 00:06:49.541
So quiet that

00:06:49.541 --> 00:06:52.041
even the voices in my head have quieted down

00:06:52.666 --> 00:06:54.041
In your head?

00:06:54.041 --> 00:06:55.416
Are there often voices?

00:06:56.041 --> 00:06:56.791
Yeah

00:06:57.166 --> 00:06:58.291
Quite often

00:06:58.791 --> 00:06:59.916
Especially when

00:07:00.666 --> 00:07:02.291
I'm not drawing as well as before

00:07:02.583 --> 00:07:03.166
or

00:07:03.166 --> 00:07:05.166
when I have absolutely no inspiration

00:07:05.458 --> 00:07:07.666
it feels like my brain screams at me every day

00:07:08.208 --> 00:07:09.041
"Enough"

00:07:09.416 --> 00:07:10.916
Does that sound funny?

00:07:12.791 --> 00:07:13.458
No

00:07:15.416 --> 00:07:16.916
Actually

00:07:17.541 --> 00:07:18.541
I'm the same

00:07:20.666 --> 00:07:22.333
You seem so steady

00:07:22.708 --> 00:07:23.541
How could that be?

00:07:27.166 --> 00:07:28.583
Because sometimes

00:07:30.666 --> 00:07:32.833
I feel like my own life

00:07:35.583 --> 00:07:37.166
has no ripples at all

00:07:38.166 --> 00:07:39.333
Every day

00:07:40.166 --> 00:07:41.708
repeating the same work

00:07:43.041 --> 00:07:44.791
dealing with similar problems

00:07:47.708 --> 00:07:49.041
After a long time

00:07:53.333 --> 00:07:54.541
even what I

00:07:54.958 --> 00:07:56.416
like

00:07:58.666 --> 00:08:01.291
and how I actually want to live

00:08:02.166 --> 00:08:03.666
have become blurry

00:08:15.291 --> 00:08:17.416
Actually, we're quite alike

00:08:17.416 --> 00:08:18.791
I've thought about it too

00:08:19.333 --> 00:08:20.833
If I didn't draw anymore

00:08:20.833 --> 00:08:22.333
who would I actually be?

00:08:22.833 --> 00:08:23.833
How would I live?

00:08:25.958 --> 00:08:27.458
Which path should I take?

00:08:39.416 --> 00:08:40.208
So

00:08:40.833 --> 00:08:41.958
what about now?

00:08:42.333 --> 00:08:43.291
How do you feel?

00:08:43.666 --> 00:08:44.708
Now

00:08:47.541 --> 00:08:50.541
I think I've discovered something new

00:08:54.291 --> 00:08:55.291
Because

00:08:56.083 --> 00:08:57.208
there is someone

00:08:57.666 --> 00:08:59.833
who makes me want to draw him every day

00:09:11.291 --> 00:09:11.833
Mm

00:09:13.708 --> 00:09:14.416
Me too

00:09:17.041 --> 00:09:18.083
These past few years

00:09:19.791 --> 00:09:21.583
it seems like my life

00:09:21.583 --> 00:09:22.916
hasn't had much light

00:09:24.166 --> 00:09:25.791
But after meeting you

00:09:26.333 --> 00:09:27.166
everything

00:09:29.291 --> 00:09:30.541
seems to have

00:09:31.083 --> 00:09:32.208
become brighter

00:09:33.208 --> 00:09:34.541
and come alive

00:09:54.833 --> 00:09:56.458
So many grapes!

00:09:56.916 --> 00:09:57.541
Meilin

00:09:59.291 --> 00:10:00.791
take a picture of me

00:10:04.916 --> 00:10:06.708
One, two, three

00:10:18.166 --> 00:10:18.875
Delicious

00:10:18.875 --> 00:10:19.416
So sweet

00:10:22.416 --> 00:10:24.791
So many

00:10:27.666 --> 00:10:28.791
One, two, three

00:10:34.791 --> 00:10:35.666
We'll take all of these

00:10:44.958 --> 00:10:45.833
Wow

00:10:45.833 --> 00:10:46.791
Look here

00:10:49.416 --> 00:10:50.166
Look

00:10:52.541 --> 00:10:53.333
Over here?

00:10:54.041 --> 00:10:54.666
Okay

00:10:54.916 --> 00:10:56.458
One, two, three

00:11:00.916 --> 00:11:01.416
One more

00:11:01.416 --> 00:11:02.583
One, two, three

00:11:03.541 --> 00:11:03.666
Good

00:11:03.666 --> 00:11:04.166
Come on

00:11:06.333 --> 00:11:06.916
Oh

00:11:06.916 --> 00:11:07.708
Careful

00:11:20.666 --> 00:11:21.541
Thanks

00:11:31.541 --> 00:11:32.958
Let me see the photo

00:11:33.791 --> 00:11:34.333
Look

00:11:35.041 --> 00:11:35.708
How is it?

00:11:36.916 --> 00:11:37.958
So cute

00:11:47.541 --> 00:11:48.541
You're here

00:11:49.166 --> 00:11:49.666
Here

00:11:50.041 --> 00:11:51.083
Hot chocolate

00:11:52.458 --> 00:11:53.166
Thanks

00:12:00.666 --> 00:12:01.208
It's good

00:12:01.708 --> 00:12:02.791
The weather's getting cold

00:12:03.291 --> 00:12:04.083
Are you cold?

00:12:05.166 --> 00:12:05.916
It's not cold.

00:12:10.291 --> 00:12:11.916
Thanks again.

00:12:13.916 --> 00:12:14.916
I know.

00:12:15.291 --> 00:12:17.666
I've often upset you with my clumsiness.

00:12:18.291 --> 00:12:18.916
But...

00:12:19.416 --> 00:12:21.458
I didn't come here just for work.

00:12:21.791 --> 00:12:24.416
I also wanted to find inspiration for myself.

00:12:25.583 --> 00:12:29.041
Maybe we can discover new stories together.

00:12:30.583 --> 00:12:31.541
Is that okay?

00:12:33.291 --> 00:12:34.791
If you have time,

00:12:35.541 --> 00:12:37.541
could you take me around Thailand

00:12:37.541 --> 00:12:39.458
to find unforgettable experiences?

00:12:39.791 --> 00:12:41.041
I want to be with you

00:12:41.041 --> 00:12:42.208
to complete this

00:12:42.833 --> 00:12:44.666
inspirational journey.

00:12:51.041 --> 00:12:52.791
I said I'd take you.

00:12:54.458 --> 00:12:55.416
Besides,

00:12:56.208 --> 00:12:57.791
starting tomorrow,

00:12:58.541 --> 00:13:00.541
I have a few days off.

00:13:01.083 --> 00:13:01.916
So,

00:13:02.541 --> 00:13:04.041
as promised,

00:13:05.291 --> 00:13:07.041
I'll take you along

00:13:07.041 --> 00:13:08.291
to find some inspiration.

00:13:08.791 --> 00:13:09.666
Really?

00:13:14.208 --> 00:13:15.833
I'll take you to a place

00:13:16.666 --> 00:13:17.541
I've wanted

00:13:17.833 --> 00:13:19.916
to go with someone.

00:13:19.916 --> 00:13:20.791
Where?

00:13:22.791 --> 00:13:24.916
Nakhon.

00:13:28.583 --> 00:13:29.375
That's great!

00:13:37.291 --> 00:13:39.000
It's so beautiful.

00:13:39.125 --> 00:13:39.625
Then,

00:13:39.625 --> 00:13:40.791
let's hurry inside.

00:13:40.791 --> 00:13:42.375
It must be even more beautiful inside.

00:13:44.208 --> 00:13:44.708
Let's go.

00:13:47.041 --> 00:13:48.625
So beautiful.

00:13:48.625 --> 00:13:51.083
When the rice turns golden,

00:13:51.333 --> 00:13:53.166
I'll definitely come back.